#: clinic/templates/clinic/index-BAD.html:492
#: clinic/templates/clinic/index.html:521
msgid ""
"Ultrasonik cihazlarla diş taşı temizliği ve diş eti sağlığı uygulamaları."
msgstr ""
"Zahnsteinreinigung mit Ultraschallgeräten und "
"Zahnfleischgesundheitsbehandlungen."

#: clinic/templates/clinic/index-BAD.html:496
#: clinic/templates/clinic/index-BAD.html:1791
#: clinic/templates/clinic/index.html:525
#: clinic/templates/clinic/index.html:2046
